lly, he turned to her, hopefully in time with a turn from her as well.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429939699";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff8c00";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299396946";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffa500";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331844;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331844";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Seabreeze";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"22";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:248:"&quot;You can see why I&#039;m concerned about her. Whatever she&#039;s in to I want to help her before she gets over her head.&quot; She&#039;d sigh and plop down on her rump. &quot;At least everything&#039;s been going smoothly for Cascade.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429939765";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0033ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299397601";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0066cc";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331847;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331847";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Milagra_Lilac";s:12:"character_id";s:1:"3";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:115:"&quot;I have to wonder what kinds of notes you are taking about what you&#039;re seeing.&quot; The voice says again";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429939929";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fb8bf8";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299399121";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#d5a9ff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331848;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331848";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"39";s:6:"handle";s:8:"Starbuck";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1341";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:142:"&quot;Is it wrong to take notes about love?&quot; Starbuck says. &quot;It&#039;s nothing risque. It&#039;s just notes for my next novel.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429939981";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#757dff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299399748";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#2b509d";s:16